This is the second making of "The Last Man On Earth" (Vincent Price) based on the book by Richard Matheson titled "I Am A Legend". Rumor has it that there is a third making of this film starring Will Smith in the works scheduled for a 2007/2008 release based on the title of the original book. This is a "must see" movie. It is superbly directed, and is an eye-opener even by todays standards. Highly recomended. If you can find "Soylent Green", another Charlton Heston movie, it is almost as equally as good.
Please seed the movie after downloading it. Thank you!
